-- Kia Motor Expects to Exceed China Sales Target of 330,000 Units This Year
-- Seonjin Cha
-- 2010-07-30T01:30:58Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-30/kia-motor-expects-to-exceed-china-sales-target-of-330-000-units-this-year.html

          
          
              Kia Motors Corp. expects to sell
more cars than it previously planned this year, helped by new
models, Treasury Director Kim Deuk Ju told reporters in Seoul
today. Kia planned to sell 330,000 units in China this year, Kim
said, without disclosing the new sales goal.  
